Subject: [PATCH 11/12] flatland_plugins: register battery plugin source
 (project-specific)

Adds src/battery.cpp to the flatland_plugins_lib sources. The
actual battery.{h,cpp} files are provided by the OpenRobOps
sim-flatland project and COPYed into place at image build time.
---
 flatland_plugins/CMakeLists.txt | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/flatland_plugins/CMakeLists.txt b/flatland_plugins/CMakeLists.txt
index eea0a40..5790b0a 100644
--- a/flatland_plugins/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/flatland_plugins/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -62,6 +62,7 @@ add_library(flatland_plugins_lib SHARED
   src/diff_drive.cpp
   src/model_tf_publisher.cpp
   src/update_timer.cpp
+  src/battery.cpp
   src/bumper.cpp
   src/tween.cpp
   src/bool_sensor.cpp
